<v δυς>¿Is anything unclear? There are a few changes to standard WebVTT incorporated in this document:

* A Unicode arrow is used alternatively with `-->` to separate the start & end times for a cue.
* Times may be relative to the previous time. `+00:00:08` means for eight seconds immediately after the previous cue ends.
* Times are kept on the [percentage clock](https://dhappy.github.io/times/).

